{"tid":960452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大圍景田苑81歲老婦墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-12-29T12:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T12:30:14.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb9c116cec1e94703077dc9c251f93f60be940da","tid":960452,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:16:45.000Z","msg":"沙田大圍景田苑恒心閣發生老婦墮樓死亡事件，今日(29日)下午約3時，上址一名保安員聽見一聲巨響，循聲走到樓外查看，赫然發現一名老婦倒臥大廈外花槽，頭爆肢折，重創昏迷，慌忙報警。救護員接報趕至，證實姓陳(81歲)女事主已死亡。現場遺下一個疑屬死者的零錢包，警方在場並無檢獲遺書，初步調查後相信陳婦從大廈天台墮下，事件並無可疑，其後聯絡死者的親友到場，親友驚聞噩耗傷心不已。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=UbsF6N3KMZ0L%2BfY1L1hhXTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=36879b8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181229/bkn-20181229154829540-1229_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181229%2Fbkn-20181229154829540-1229_00822_001.html&d=UbsF6N3KMZ0L%2BfY1L1hhXTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=c311b9cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181229/bkn-20181229154829540-1229_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"15b40c4b52d27984f40f6303c076748ea47fa896","tid":960452,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:19:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8647f229114f3bdc6bd736e36c5ccaa2beb285e1","tid":960452,"uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:20:28.000Z","msg":"又少個$2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de